casebody.data:
Tuesday, January 23, 1996

MOTION DOCKET

96-131. Lemaster v. Radcliff.

Pickaway County, No. 95CA25. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Pickaway County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to reduce bail,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to reduce bad be, and hereby is, denied, effective January 22, 1996.
